{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f2c1f23aa5","title":"致卫立焊电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"375624e947","index":0,"year":1941,"month":5,"day":26,"articleId":"f2c1f23aa5"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji16","name":"毛泽东全集第16卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji16.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji16":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b58be51734","type":"paragraph","text":"致卫立焊电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"f2c1f23aa5"},{"id":"f265ebf765","type":"paragraph","text":"（1941年5月26日）目前性有国共团结并在蒋委员长领导之下实行亲苏外交，坚持抗日到底，方能换救危亡，美国是靠不住的，日、美、华妥协阴课必须拒绝。我们所希望于国民党的只是（甲）坚持抗日：（乙）民主政治：（丙）改善国共关系这样三点而已。关于改善国共关系又分三点，即（甲）对新四军问题予以解决：（乙）对八路军销弹予以发给：（丙）对反共言论与反共行动予以停止。除此以外，并无其他要求。特同卫长官与胡宗南先生会见，时间约定后，我们即派南汉意来洛，共商团结对敌大计。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"f2c1f23aa5"}],"page":{"id":"67a72bfeb8","publicationId":"maoquanji16","articleId":"f2c1f23aa5","start":106,"end":106}}}},"__N_SSG":true}